column30: To help me in my diet and help me track my calorie intake so I can live a more healthy lifestyle. MyFitness pal is also used for me to get into shape and get my dream body so I can have more confidence in myself socially.
column31: The major challenge I faced while using a food journaling application is that I have a hard time measuring the quantity of food I eat. I also have a hard time choosing what type of food as there are too many selections out there. The macros are also sometimes not visible.
column32: The advantage of using a food journaling application is that it helps you live a more healthy lifestyle. It helps to get into shape and get your dream body so you can have more confidence. It helps you track food macros and calories so you can eat healthier.
column33: The key feature I find lacking in my food journaling application is a wider variety of foods, mostly local Filipino foods as it is hard to keep track of homemade Filipino foods. There is also a lack in QR code scanner as not all brands are not scanned in it.
column34: The only thing I can say is overall, I am highly satisfied with myFitness pal as the application is generally helpful and it helps me keep track of my calories. It is basic and helps me keep track of my weight and the application is smooth to use.

column33: These types of apps need tutorials to understand the operation of each option, how to measure the quantities, a calendar or any option where you can have a balanced eating plan
column34: I feel very happy, I send you my greetings and I also congratulate the entire team that works to improve this app every day, I love how its design encourages me to continue fighting against my overweight. I hope you can continue with this useful work, it really manages to change lives

column30: The primary motivation of using this app is to follow a healthy lifestyle which is the ultimate need of today. Today there is a lot of junk food available here and there which I would say is very dangerous to our health and body as well. I faced this problem seriously myself before I resolute to be conscious about my health and nutritional supplements and dietary plans . The app has been since then very helpful and beneficial for me. Tracking my food logs and following my dietary plans accordingly since then has become an ease and essential part of my lifestyle. Now I care a lot about my food and am extremely conscious as well.
column31: The major challenges are to use the app every day without missing a single day so that I can maintain the full record of the food that goes inside my belly. Though it had a reminder which proved to be quite handy and I was generally able to record most of the data related to my food. The search function could have been a bit better in the app I reckon though so that it may become hassle free. For every food item there should have been apt alternative so that we may find it easier to find food of a particular type and follow the correct plan which suits our lifestyles and health. The ui of the app should have been even more attractive to gain more attention though it was fair enough. I found the app to be quite good and helpful so far.
column32:
The advantage are-
I can easily find the food items by search option and find the food in the list. The amount or quantity can be changed so we get correct calorie counter and other nutritional status . The ui of the app is very basic and simply even for a very simple and basic user who is worried about his diet and food intake. The biggest advantage however is the reminder option which reminds about the time and food that we should follow for a specific dietary supplements or dietary plans in order to maintain to healthy lifestyle. The app is easily available for most of the users and it has proven to be quite beneficial thus far.
column33: Missing key feature - There are many apps which give an option to search food with image and voice input, but the version of the app I use doea not provide any options of the image search options and thus I have to do some hard work of putting lot of text input to get my desired results. It some times become frustrating as well. I hope they update the app so that the search option will include image option also. That's a major change i would like to see in my food journaling app. The are some food items also there which are found in a particular region but the search option does not list them in the results. That is disappointing also especially for me who take lot of local food from local shops around here in my locality.
column34: There is a generally good or I would say a fair user experience thus far of using this app for myself. I have had bad eating habits and I preferred a lot of junk food in the past and hence malsufferred a lot . The shape of my body wasn't very appealing because of this. I wanted to change all this and decided to follow a severely strict diet plan and then I downloaded the app. I now become very conscious vigilant about the calorie intake plus nutritional benefits. Within a month I was controlling and managing every thing well. I feel great now. No junk food and tracking my nutritional plans are far better now and easier as well. I am quite satisfied with the progress I made so far using this app. I hope an update would further make the app more convenient and user friendly.
